{"word":"翱","detail":[{"title":"基本字义解释","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"● "},{"type":"strong","content":"翱"},{"type":"span","content":"áoㄠˊ","class":["pinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎ 〔"},{"type":"span","content":"翱","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"翔〕展开翅膀在天空回旋地飞，如“雄鹰在天空"},{"type":"span","content":"翱翔","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"”。"}]]},{"title":"英文翻译","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"soar, roam"}]]},{"title":"详细字义解释","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"◎ "},{"type":"strong","content":"翱"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"áo","class":["pinyin"]},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"img","content":"","class":["sound"]},{"type":"text","content":" "}],[{"type":"span","content":"〈动词〉","class":["parts"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"(1) (形声。从羽,皋声。本义:翅膀上下振动而回旋地飞)"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(2) 同本义"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"翱,翱翔也。——《说文》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"思从祥风翱。——《汉书·王褒传》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"翱翔四海之外。——《淮南子·览冥》。注:“翼一上一下曰翱。”"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"鸟之高飞,翼上下曰翱,直剌不动曰翔。——《淮南子·俶真》注"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"齐子翱翔。——《诗·齐风·载驱》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"羔裘翱翔。——《诗·桧风·羔裘》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"逸翮后尘,翱翥先路。——鲍照《舞鹤赋》"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(3) 又如:翱翥(飞翔的样子)"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(4) 喻人自由自在地遨游,游乐"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"将翱将翔。——《诗·郑风·女曰鸡鸣》"}]]},{"title":"常用词组","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"翱翔"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"áoxiáng","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"在空中(常指在高空)飞行或盘旋"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"展翅翱翔于两三千米高空的雄鹰,一下子就能发现地面上宽广范围内的一只小兔或小鸡。——《眼睛与仿生学》"}]]},{"title":"说文解字","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"【卷四】【羽部】"},{"type":"span","content":"翱","class":["kszi"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"翱翔也。从羽皐聲。五牢切"}]]},{"title":"字源演变","content":[]},{"title":"同音字","content":[]}],"type":"通用字","pinyin":["áo"],"radical":"羽","stroke":"十画","total_stroke":"十六画","stroke_order":"ノ丨フ一一一ノ丶一丨フ丶一フ丶一","input_method":{"bopomofo":"HJSMM","number":"27420","unicode":"U+7FF1","wubi":"RDFN"}}